{"tid":138396,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(書友更加入嚟)請問大家邊到有得賣藏書票","createTime":"2017-02-28T14:17:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-28T15:59:38.000Z","uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5ef8df24249829cf793c8f3d0edf05eab87864d","tid":138396,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-28T14:17:47.000Z","msg":"藏書票可以說一種小型的版畫，本來是用來貼在書本封面內外，作為自己藏書的標誌，和藏書印一樣。透過一張刻畫有圖案的版，我們用油墨或其他顏料將版面的圖形轉印在紙張上，這就是「版畫」。版畫可大可小，大的可以做到如全開或二全開甚至四全開般大小，也可以只做數吋大小或數公分大小的迷你版畫，而「藏書票」即是類似迷你版畫的一種微型版畫。一般人會把藏書票貼在愛書的扉頁裏，標示書籍擁有者的身分；也有人專門四處蒐集藏書票，把它當作收藏品般地珍藏。<br />\n(From wiki)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NF3X3yz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNF3X3yz.jpg&h=816a41a7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/221655_190563dd8ed66a72e72bdcd38e303104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F221655_190563dd8ed66a72e72bdcd38e303104.jpg&h=8717ba38&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/221656_8bc78a6b2aa52010aec21c3fb11b8b92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F221656_8bc78a6b2aa52010aec21c3fb11b8b92.jpg&h=06775018&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/28/221657_dc83b0874b967c5b898d5bfde7bd3767.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F28%2F221657_dc83b0874b967c5b898d5bfde7bd3767.jpg&h=faad7c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n想問全能嘅連登仔知唔知邊到有/有得訂購/有人製作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我ig/google search咗好多都唔見有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自己本身鐘意收藏書"},{"pid":"ed0ee0a3c6a70e9c046123ebf72833caa7554bcf","tid":138396,"uid":1554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0